From 28497cac0cafaecb9bdfeb81d9f0060a04cd71b6 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Pavankumar Nandeshwar <quic_pnandesh@quicinc.com>
Date: Tue, 18 Mar 2025 14:36:58 +0530
Subject: [PATCH 2/8] wifi: ath12k: Move arch specific rx code to wifi7
 directory

Move arch specific RX data path to wifi7 directory as part of unified driver
framework.

With this, RX datapath can be optimized for a specific
architecture (wifi7/wifi8 etc).

The new APIs will be a part of dp_rx.c file inside wifi7 directory.
wifi7/dp_rx.c file will continue to be part of ath12k.ko
temporarily until the corresponding infra for movement
to ath12k_wifi7.ko arrives in upcoming patches.

APIs being moved:
ath12k_dp_rx_h_enctype
ath12k_dp_rx_h_decap_type
ath12k_dp_rx_h_mesh_ctl_present
